  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Liberia: Promoting Increased Accountability for Sexual and Gender-Based Violence</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1) To enhance the efficiency, transparency, and accountability of Criminal Court E through targeted support to judges, court staff, and other relevant actors; 2) To enhance the capacity of offices under the Court Administrator to support efficient, transparent, and accountable processing of SGBV cases by Criminal Court E; 3) To improve access to justice and protection mechanisms for SGBV survivors; 4) To increase the education of women in the Liberian National Police (LNP).</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="3">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Judges, court staff, and other relevant actors; SGBV survivors and Liberian National Police (LNP).</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aimed to enhance the efficiency, transparency and accountability of the Montserrado County Criminal Court &#x201C;E&#x201D; on the one hand, and improve access to justice and protection mechanisms for victims of sexual and gender-based violence on the other.</narrative>
  </description>
